<item>
            <title>[LU-6868] MDT migration does not generate changelog records</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-6868</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Migrating a file between MDTs does not generate a changelog record. Since migration changes the FID of the file, the absence of changelog records make it difficult for tools such as Robinhood to track the state of filesystems on which migration is used.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
